---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SEOHead from '../../components/SEOHead.astro';
import Navbar from '../../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout>
  <SEOHead slot="head" title="Tattoo Shop Inventory Management Guide — 2026 | InkFlow Blog" description="Learn how to manage tattoo shop inventory. Track ink, needles, and supplies with low-stock alerts. Never run out mid-session." />
  <Navbar />

  <article class="pt-24 pb-16 sm:pt-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <p class="text-sm text-accent-400 mb-4">May 28, 2026</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-white sm:text-4xl">Tattoo Shop Inventory Management Guide</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-400">Running out of ink mid-session costs you time and money. Here's how to keep your supplies organized and never run out of what you need.</p>
    </div>
  </article>

  <section class="border-t border-ink-800/50 py-12">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 prose prose-invert">
      <h2>Why Inventory Management Matters</h2>
      <p>Running out of a specific ink color or needle cartridge mid-session means lost time, frustrated artists, and delayed appointments. Most studios lose $200-500 per month on emergency supply runs alone.</p>
      <p><a href="/features/inventory" class="text-accent-400 hover:underline">InkFlow's inventory system</a> tracks every item with low-stock alerts so you always know what needs reordering.</p>

      <h2>What to Track</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Ink bottles by color and brand</li>
        <li>Needle cartridges by size and type</li>
        <li>Gloves, masks, and disposables</li>
        <li>Aftercare products for retail</li>
        <li>Machine parts and tubes</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Set Low-Stock Alerts</h2>
      <p>Define minimum quantities for every item. When stock drops below the threshold, you get notified automatically. No more emergency runs to the supply store.</p>

      <h2>Track Cost Per Session</h2>
      <p>Know exactly how much each appointment costs in supplies. This helps you price services accurately and identify which items are eating into your margins.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-12 text-center border-t border-ink-800/50">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Track Your Inventory with InkFlow</h2>
    <a href="https://app.ink-flows.com/register" class="mt-6 inline-block rounded-lg bg-accent-500 px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-ink-950 hover:bg-accent-400 transition-all">Try InkFlow Free</a>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
